Introduction.en: The Zombies are going to hold the first "Zombie Carnival" ever in history. After a fair and democratic vote, they decided to have it in your house. Additionally, Dr. Zomboss handpicked 100 greatest imp pilots to drive the Gargantuar Primes!
Introduction.zh-CN: 僵尸们即将举行史上第一次“僵尸狂欢节”。经过公平民主的投票，他们决定将地点定在你的房子。僵尸博士还亲自挑选了最优秀的100位小鬼驾驶巨尸统领者！
